The Dutch East India Company was the worlds first multinational corporation and the first company to issue stock.

Their coins, or duits, are also known as New Yorks First Cent as the Dutch originally settled New Amsterdam, the capital of New Netherlands.

These cuff links are crafted from coins minted by the Dutch East India Company (VOC) from 1726-1804. Coins set in sterling silver 3-prong setting with swivel findings. Measures approximately 7/8" in diameter. Made in USA and Mexico.

Each pair of cuff links comes gift-boxed with a Certificate of Authenticity.

Product.Description: Times of your life- the ultimate birthday book
Product.ExtendedDescription:
With a festive red cover perfect for holiday gifting, this unique book contains every birthday or anniversary front page in someone's life. A thoughtful and one-of-a-kind gift, this book can also commemorate other important dates for any milestone day of your choosing.

Exclusively available from The New York Times Store, this holly-red hardbound book is personalized with the recipients name in gold lettering on the cover for a personal touch. The 12" x 15" book also includes a fascinating 19-page timeline of twentieth-century events, ten blank pages for personal mementos, a magnifier, a certificate of authenticity and a commemorative Times coin. The perfect companion showpiece, the solid bronze birthday coin is engraved with the books selected date on one side, and the renowned New York Times Tower on the reverse.

If ordering for this year's birthday or anniversary, be sure to order the day of birthday or later to include this year's page.

Made in U.S. - Ships in 1 - 3 days.

Product.ProductName: BellEvolve Duo Stem Cell Serum - Younger Looking Skin
Product.Description: BellEvolve Duo Stem Cell Serum Apple & Citrus Stem Cells
Product.ExtendedDescription:
Younger, more luminous skin, with plant stem cell technology!

Our BellEvolve Duo Stem Cell Serum contains both apple and orange stems cells... PhytoCellTec(tm) Malus Domestica and Citrustem(tm)




PhytoCellTec(tm) Malus Domestica produces younger looking skin.
Epidermal stem cells retain their vitality longer and are capable of forming new tissue and renewing the skin.

With Citrustem(tm) the skin regains the elastic properties of a skin 12 years younger.
The skin appears renewed, wrinkles are reduced, and its global aspect is improved.

This is a DYNAMIC DUO for anti aging!


Apple Stem Cells - PhytoCellTec(tm) Malus Domestica

The Uttwiler Spatlauber is an old Swiss variety, which is very rare today. It was known for its exceptional capacity to keep for long periods but gradually lost its popularity to sweet apples because of its bitter taste. As the apple could be stored for a long time without becoming shriveled or losing flavor, it clearly had special ingredients and especially long-lived stem cells. And precisely these longevity factors were of particular interest to the researchers at Mibelle Biochemistry.

Plant stem cells for skin stem cells
The development of the innovative PhytoCellTec(tm) technology made possible to grow plant stem cells on a large scale. It also became possible to effectively cultivate rare and endangered plants like the Uttwiler Spatlauber. PhytoCellTec(tm) made plant stem cells available for cosmetics for the first time.

Improves the vitality of stem cells
Cultures of epidermal stem cells were treated with different concentrations of PhytoCellTec(tm) Malus Domestica and their colony-forming efficiency was determined. The investigations showed that PhytoCellTec (tm) Malus Domestica had a clear, positive effect on stem cell characteristics.

Preserves the ability to form new epidermal tissue
Young, vital epidermal stem cells can form a complete, multi-layer epidermis in laboratory conditions. When this experiment is conducted on older stem cells, these no longer multiply and no epidermis is formed. These stem cells are depleted and have reached the end of their lifecycle. If, however, Malus Domestica stem cell extract is added to cultivate the stem cells, even old stem cells can still generate a stratified epidermis. Under the influence of Malus Domestica stem cell extract, the epidermal stem cells retain their vitality longer and are capable of forming new tissue and renewing the skin.


The Oranges - Citrustem(tm) - Developed by Provitol Group

Organizes and redensifies the dermis structure.  Restores the extracellular network improving cells adhesion. Recovers the quality of a young skin.

With Citrustem(tm) the skin regains the elastic properties of a skin 12 years younger.


Citrustem(tm) from orange stem cells, increases the expression of genes capable of improving the structure of the extracellular matrix (ECM).

Citrustem(tm) organizes and redensifies the dermis structure, by increasing the synthesis of the elements forming the extracellular matrix.

A structured dermis translates into a regular and defined micro relief.  The skin recovers its smooth and velvety feel.

The skin appears renewed, wrinkles are reduced, and its global aspect is improved.  It looks younger.
